		"description": {
			"value": "<p>Wondrous Item - Uncommon</p><p><em>This deceptive dust looks identical to @UUID[Compendium.dnd5e.equipment24.Item.dmgDustOfDisappe]{Dust of Disappearance}, but it seizes the lungs of nearby creatures.</em></p><p><strong>Action</strong> - 30 ft Emanation (Self) - Consumed</p><p><strong>[[/save CON 15]]{Constitution Save (DC 15)}</strong></p><p>&amp;reference[Constructs], &amp;reference[Elementals], &amp;reference[Oozes], &amp;reference[Plants], and &amp;reference[Undead] automatically succeed. Creature who used is rolls the save as well.</p><ul><li><p><strong>Failure:</strong> The creature starts violently sneezing, becoming &amp;reference[Incapacitated] and beginning to suffocate. An affected creature repeats the saving throw at the end of each of its turns, ending the effect on itself on a success. The effect ends early if the creature receives a <em>@UUID[Compendium.elkan5e.elkan5e-spells.Item.gQCBKxTyZeqCvy0D]{Lesser Restoration}</em> spell.</p></li><li><p><strong>Success:</strong> The creature is unaffected.</p></li></ul>",
